        {
          "target": "long_description",
          "old_value": "Jovia is a social app designed to help you discover new people, share moments, and start conversations in a relaxed, natural way.<br><br>Whether you\u2019re looking to expand your social circle, chat with interesting people, or simply explore what others are sharing, Jovia gives you an easy space to connect\u2014without pressure or expectations.<br><br> Discover People &amp; Stories<br><br>Browse profiles, explore shared moments, and get a glimpse into the lives of people around you. Everyone has a story\u2014Jovia makes it easy to discover and engage with them.<br><br>Start Conversations Naturally<br><br>See someone interesting? Say hi and start a conversation when it feels right. Jovia is built around simple, respectful communication that lets connections grow at their own pace.<br><br>Share Your Moments<br><br>Post photos, thoughts, or updates to express who you are. Sharing moments helps others get to know you beyond just a profile.<br> <br>A Comfortable &amp; Safe Space<br><br>Jovia is designed for adults and focuses on creating a positive, welcoming environment. We encourage respectful interactions and give you control over your experience.",
          "new_value": "Jovia \u2013 Real Dates Start Here<br><br>Jovia is a dating app built for people who want more than endless chatting.<br>It\u2019s for those who are ready to meet in real life and go on meaningful dates.<br><br>We believe real connections happen face to face. Jovia helps you match, talk, and move naturally toward meeting in person \u2014 without games or pressure.<br><br>\u2764\ufe0f Designed for Real Dates<br><br>Jovia focuses on helping you meet people who are genuinely interested in dating. Browse profiles, see who\u2019s interested, and start conversations with purpose.<br><br>\ud83d\udcac Talk First, Meet When It Feels Right<br><br>Get to know each other through chat, then take the next step and plan a real date when you\u2019re ready. No rushing \u2014 just honest connections.<br><br>\ud83d\udccd Meet in Real Life<br><br>Jovia encourages real-world meetings, making it easier to turn online conversations into in-person dates. Because chemistry is best felt offline.<br><br>\ud83d\udd12 A Respectful Dating Experience<br><br>Jovia is designed for adults and promotes respectful, authentic interactions. You stay in control of who you talk to and when you meet.<br><br>Privacy: https://sites.google.com/view/privacypolicyforlovia<br>Terms: https://sites.google.com/view/terms-of-service-for-lovia<br>Visit: https://loviaandroid.com/",
          "version": "",
